The paper deals with the construction of sequential circuits from regular expressions, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and formal languages (cs.FL). The paper also discusses the use of automata, which is a topic related to data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.LG). Finally, the paper presents performance results, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
